data.description: This spacious 4 bedroom, 2.5 bath is situated on a private, 2 acre lot in a convenient location. It offers an oversized living room and dining area, wood burning fireplace, spacious kitchen with SS Appliance, Kitchen island, Solid surface countertops, and a mud room with a half bath. The title has been retired and It is on a permanent foundation. No HOA! Convenient to Schools, shopping and restaurants. Call today to schedule your appointment.
